comments.body:
So I can ask the same question again - if there will one day be several of these, do they want to be in their own struct?

e.g.

```
type CSIDriver {
  //...
  StorageCapacity *StorageCapacityParams
  OtherFeature *OtherFeatureParams
  YetAnother *YetAnotherParams
}
```

vs

```
type CSIDriver {
  //...
  Features *CSIDriverFeatures
}

type CSIDriverFeatures {
  StorageCapacity *StorageCapacityParams
  OtherFeature *OtherFeatureParams
  YetAnother *YetAnotherParams
}
```

Something is still optional...

